    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and is ideal for someone prioritizing utility and mechanical reliability over cosmetic perfection. The exterior shows its age with several noticeable scratches, a few small dings, and some fading in the clear coat on the roof. Inside, the upholstery has visible wear and a few minor stains, though all electronics and climate controls remain functional. Mechanically, the car is dependable, having undergone regular oil changes and recent brake service, ensuring it is ready for daily commuting.",
      "price": 19800.0,
