    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "We are pleased to present this exemplary vehicle, maintained in absolute showroom condition. This specimen exhibits a level of preservation that is exceedingly rare, featuring a flawless exterior finish and an interior that remains entirely indistinguishable from new. Meticulously curated and subjected to rigorous standards of care, this automobile represents a premier acquisition for the most discerning investor or enthusiast. We invite you to inspect a vehicle that truly defines the standard for pre-owned excellence.",
      "price": 48500.0,
