    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is a true time capsule, maintained to a standard rarely seen on the secondary market. The exterior finish is absolutely flawless, boasting a deep, mirror-like gloss with zero rock chips, swirl marks, or imperfections, thanks to a professional ceramic coating and consistent climate-controlled garage storage. Inside, the cabin remains in showroom state; the premium leather upholstery shows no signs of wear, creases, or bolster compression, and it retains that distinct new-car aroma. Every electronic feature, sensor, and driver-assist system functions exactly as intended. Mechanically, this car is beyond reproach, with a comprehensive service history performed exclusively by certified technicians at the original dealership. It has never seen a car wash brush or been driven in inclement weather. For the discerning buyer who demands perfection and a 'no-excuses' vehicle, this example stands alone. Sold with all original keys, manuals, and a clean title in hand.",
      "price": 46500.0,
